.SH NAME
Number.NEGATIVE_INFINITY \- Number.NEGATIVE_INFINITY
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]Number.NEGATIVE_INFINITY\f[B]\f[R] static data property
represents the negative Infinity value.
.SH VALUE
The same as the negative value of the global \f[CR]Infinity\f[R]
property.
.PP
